ation growth will end.'),(516,'video-1-subtitles','We will be around 10 Billion people in the year 2100.'),(517,'video-1-subtitles','So, three Billion more.'),(518,'video-1-subtitles','Where will they live?'),(519,'video-1-subtitles','No more Billion in America.'),(520,'video-1-subtitles','No more in Europe.'),(521,'video-1-subtitles','One more in Asia.'),(522,'video-1-subtitles','And most probably, two Billion more in Africa.'),(523,'video-1-subtitles','By the time the population growth is over,'),(524,'video-1-subtitles','there will be one, one, three, five Billion.'),(525,'video-1-subtitles','So the experts say that the African population will triple,'),(526,'video-1-subtitles','from one Billion to three Billion.'),(527,'video-1-subtitles','When people hear that, the most common reaction is: \"That´s impossible!\"'),(528,'video-1-subtitles','When I went to school, the Asian population was bit more than one Billion.'),(529,'video-1-subtitles','And the experts said, within 50 years, the Asian population will triple.'),(530,'video-1-subtitles','And the common reaction was: \"That´s impossible!\"'),(531,'video-1-subtitles','This is the number of people today.'),(532,'video-1-subtitles','Look at Asia: the experts were right.'),(533,'video-1-subtitles','And most likely, the same thing will happen in Africa,'),(534,'video-1-subtitles','before population growth stops.'),(535,'video-1-subtitles','So, this is South America. North America.'),(536,'video-1-subtitles','West Europe. East Europe.'),(537,'video-1-subtitles','The people of North America and West Europe'),(538,'video-1-subtitles','have dominated World Economy for a long time.'),(539,'video-1-subtitles','In the future they will only be 10 percent of World population.'),(540,'video-1-subtitles','By the end of population growth,'),(541,'video-1-subtitles','80 percent will be living in Asia and Africa.'),(542,'a-VideoFile-subtitles',NULL),(543,'a-VideoFile-subtitles',NULL),(544,'a-VideoFile-subtitles',NULL),(545,'a-Vi